title: 820-00165 Won't power without Magsafe 2 (can't use Magsage 1 w/ adapter)
message: Liquid damaged board, got it up and running but it won't charge/turn on without an 85w magsafe 2. Otherwise it runs flawlessly. Is this something pretty common?

title: 820-00165 Won't power without Magsafe 2 (can't use Magsage 1 w/ adapter)
message: Your customer will never try to use a magsafe 1 on this, just let it be if it works with a magsafe 2.
